### Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/health

###

### ============================================
### MUTATIONS - VTL Resolvers + DynamoDB
### ============================================

### Create User (VTL + DynamoDB)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation CreateUser($input: CreateUserInput!) { createUser(input: $input) { id name email createdAt } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "name": "John Doe",
      "email": "john@example.com"
    }
  }
}

###

### Delete User (VTL + DynamoDB)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation DeleteUser($id: ID!) { deleteUser(id: $id) }",
  "variables": {
    "id": "some-user-id"
  }
}

###

### ============================================
### QUERIES - VTL Resolvers + DynamoDB
### ============================================

### Get User by ID (VTL + DynamoDB)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetUser($id: ID!) { getUser(id: $id) { id name email createdAt updatedAt } }",
  "variables": {
    "id": "some-user-id"
  }
}

###

### List All Users (VTL + DynamoDB)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { listUsers { id name email createdAt } }"
}

