### MUTATIONS - JS Resolvers + .NET Lambda
### ============================================

### Process Order (JS Resolver + .NET Lambda)
POST http://localhost:4000/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation ProcessOrder($id: ID!) { processOrder(id: $id) { id status createdAt } }",
  "variables": {
    "id": "order-123"
  }
}

